{"tid":193730,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人雖然身邊有好多朋友但....","createTime":"2017-04-09T13:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T13:45:54.000Z","uid":55989,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49785bf5dc41d64f458d90dc9b581c356ca7e806","tid":193730,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人平日比人既感覺係好多朋友<br />\n但其實內心會覺得自己好孤獨？<br />\n自問對人算真心 <br />\n亦同意對人唔需要有咩回報<br />\n但有時都忍唔住會諗<br />\n點解其他人唔開心果陣有人關心<br />\n但當自己唔開心果陣 <br />\n人地會覺得唔需要 <br />\n或者唔會去關心自己<br />\n雖然口口聲聲話<br />\n要做一個可以照亮別人的人 <br />\n其實最需要照亮的 反而係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898d10bcdff9ebb39f3195e82c8b16091947901c","tid":193730,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60fd81a87f6f85c8660ef15d256781fe1296b69","tid":193730,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:32:20.000Z","msg":"因為冇人知你唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22995cdc312492183b7cdda362ee2ba00d059b3","tid":193730,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:33:15.000Z","msg":"我總是一個人在練習一個人"},{"pid":"c363d1295c0755806dd792ff9f040c66115bfc52","tid":193730,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為冇人知你唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前都會覺得要同人分享自己想法 <br />\n人地先會明自己點諗 <br />\n但發現人地其實唔太想聽<br />\n放負容易 收負難 <br />\n久而久之都唔想麻煩到人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6429e8a1330cc80829dfc2867ee8a6f445a142cc","tid":193730,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我總是一個人在練習一個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開始慢慢習慣了<br />\n最近開心的原因 好多都係因為人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到朋友拍拖 自己都替佢開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d56ebfa332657eb4ebb0271abf444f7b3552f0","tid":193730,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"已習慣一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e714fd989f451b9faa23071dea5df177f8b87b7c","tid":193730,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已習慣一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  每個人都有d過去"}]}